
===========================================
Tar Files
===========================================

Extracting tar files 

$ tar -xf files.tar

-- add -v (verbose) to see in action

to list the contents on a tar use -t 

to extart to a different dir use -c 

you can only extract certian if you want 

$ tar -xf files.tar file1.txt file2.txt

and/ or use wildcards. 

$ tar -xf files.tar --wildcards '*.txt'


